trans-unit.source: Represents a license that enables access to protected rights managed content.
trans-unit.target: Representerar en licens som ger åtkomst till skyddade rättighetsskyddat innehåll.

trans-unit.source: As with other <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement> types, UseLicense is only usable in full trust applications.
trans-unit.target: Precis som med andra <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement>typer, UseLicense kan endast användas i program med fullständigt förtroende.</xref:System.Security.RightsManagement>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: A use license in serialized [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_xrml](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] form.
trans-unit.target: En användarlicens i serialiseras [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_xrml](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] formuläret.

trans-unit.source: useLicense is .
trans-unit.target: useLicenseis .

trans-unit.source: useLicense is invalid.
trans-unit.target: useLicenseär ogiltigt.

trans-unit.source: Gets the application data dictionary that contains key/value pairs passed from the publishing application to the consuming application.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar datamappen i program som innehåller nyckel/värde-par som överförts från publishing programmet till den konsumerande appen.

trans-unit.source: One data key/value pair that is processed by a Rights Management Services (RMS) server is the string pair "Allow_Server_Editing"/"True".
trans-unit.target: En nyckel/värde-par som bearbetas av en Rights Management Services (RMS)-server är paret strängen "Allow_Server_Editing" / "True".

trans-unit.source: When the issuance license "Allow_Server_Editing"/"True" is set, the service, or any trusted service, can reuse the content key.
trans-unit.target: När utfärdandet licens "Allow_Server_Editing" / "True" anges tjänsten eller någon tillförlitlig tjänst kan återanvända innehållsnyckeln.

trans-unit.source: The key/value pair "NOLICCACHE" / "1" controls the Use License embedding policy of consuming applications.
trans-unit.target: Nyckel/värde-par "NOLICCACHE" / "1" styr användningslicens bädda in princip användarprogram.

trans-unit.source: When "NOLICCACHE" / "1" is set, applications are expected not to embed the Use License within the rights managed document.
trans-unit.target: När "NOLICCACHE" / "1" har angetts, program förväntas inte bädda in användarlicens inom rättigheter hanterat dokument.

trans-unit.source: The application data dictionary that contains key/value pairs passed from the publishing application to the consuming application.
trans-unit.target: Datamappen i program som innehåller nyckel/värde-par som skickas från publishing programmet till den konsumerande appen.

trans-unit.source: Binds the license to a given <xref href="System.Security.RightsManagement.SecureEnvironment"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Binder licens till en viss <xref href="System.Security.RightsManagement.SecureEnvironment"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: After the license is bound to a secure environment, the application can examine and exercise the rights granted by the license.
trans-unit.target: När licensen är bunden till en säker miljö, kan programmet undersöka och utöva de rättigheter som licensen.

trans-unit.source: The returned <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.CryptoProvider> instance provides decryption and access to the protected rights managed content.
trans-unit.target: Den returnerade <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.CryptoProvider>instans innehåller dekryptering och åtkomst till det skyddade rättighetsskyddat innehållt.</xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.CryptoProvider>

trans-unit.source: The environment to bind the license to.
trans-unit.target: Miljö att binda licens till.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Security.RightsManagement.CryptoProvider"></xref> instance if the license binding succeeded; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Security.RightsManagement.CryptoProvider"> </xref> instans om licensens bindning lyckades, i annat fall <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: secureEnvironment is .
trans-unit.target: secureEnvironmentis .

trans-unit.source: Gets the content identifier created by the publisher.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar innehåll ID som skapas av utgivaren.

trans-unit.source: ContentId is created by the publisher and can be used to match content to a <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense> and <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.PublishLicense>.
trans-unit.target: ContentId skapas av utgivaren och kan användas för att matcha en innehåll <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense>och <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.PublishLicense>.</xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.PublishLicense> </xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense>

trans-unit.source: The content identifier created by the publisher.
trans-unit.target: Innehåll identifierare som skapats av utgivaren.

trans-unit.source: Indicates if this license is equivalent to another given license.
trans-unit.target: Anger om denna licens motsvarar en annan angivna licens.

trans-unit.source: Equals tests for equivalence comparing the serialized [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_xrml](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] strings specified to the <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense.%23ctor%2A> constructors.
trans-unit.target: Är lika med tester för att jämföra den serialiserade likvärdiga [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_xrml](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] strängar som angetts för den <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense.%23ctor%2A>konstruktorer.</xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense.%23ctor%2A>

trans-unit.source: The license to compare.
trans-unit.target: Licensen för att jämföra.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if both licenses are the equivalent; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Om båda licenser är likvärdiga, Annars <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Returns the hash code associated with this license.
trans-unit.target: Returnerar den hash-kod som är associerad med denna licens.

trans-unit.source: The returned hash code is based on the serialized [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_xrml](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] string passed to the <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense.%23ctor%2A> constructor.
trans-unit.target: Returnerade hash-koden är baserad på den serialiserade [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_xrml](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] sträng skickades till den <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense.%23ctor%2A>konstruktor.</xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense.%23ctor%2A>

trans-unit.source: A hash code for this license.
trans-unit.target: En hash-kod för denna licens.

trans-unit.source: Gets the owner of the license.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar ägaren av licensen.

trans-unit.source: The license owner is obtained from the serialized [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_xrml](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] string passed to the <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense.%23ctor%2A> constructor.
trans-unit.target: Licensägaren hämtas från den serialiserade [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_xrml](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] sträng skickades till den <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense.%23ctor%2A>konstruktor.</xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense.%23ctor%2A>

trans-unit.source: The owner of the license.
trans-unit.target: Ägaren av licensen.

trans-unit.source: Returns the serialized [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xrml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xrml-md.md)] string used to create this license.
trans-unit.target: Returnerar den serialiserade [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xrml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xrml-md.md)] sträng som används för att skapa denna licens.

trans-unit.source: The serialized [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_xrml](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] string originally passed to the <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense.%23ctor%2A> constructor.
trans-unit.target: Den serialiserade [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_xrml](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] sträng som ursprungligen skickades till den <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense.%23ctor%2A> konstruktor.
